Max Massacre

MC: Max Massacre

M Female: Ilyana? (harpy, mace tail, wings, etc.)

**Male (actually female): Sir Chapstick (nickname)
Poses as a male because females can't become knights.
Nicknamed Sir Chapstick for "his" femininity.
Awkward relationship with other knights because "he" makes them question their sexuality.
Sent to keep an eye on Max.


Story
Unfortunately named hero, everyone assumes he's a villain.
Tries to do good, misunderstood, hated, run out of town.
Coaxed by M Female, Max sets off to become a hero.
Prove to town that he's a hero after all by accomplishing a great feat and returning.

*returns in their time of need; impending evil threatens to take over the town.